===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#{{time}} An [[instrument]] used to measure or keep track of [[time]].
# {{slang}} [[odometer|Odometer]] of a vehicle. ''This car has over 300,000 miles on the '''clock'''.''
# the fluffy seed head of a [[dandelion]] flower.

